doc.previous: The Vasa Committee was established to investigate the possibility of raising and preserving the ship and Franz n persuaded the navy the National Heritage Board the National Maritime Museum and a large private salvage company the Neptune Company to back the project They began exploratory dives in the fall of 1956 and discussed how the ship might be raised 39
